comments.content: This is indeed a freeware/shareware font. I remember seeing it on a font site some 3 years ago. I used to have it, even... but that was many hdds ago, and I don't remember the name anymore.
awwww, lets go freeware font again.
Cheshire Dave might know this one. From what I've seen, he's pretty good when it comes to identifying freeware fonts.

I think it's Bjork. It's the last one on this page.
